---
title: Cumberland Sausages & Root Veg Mash with Rosemary Carrots and Red Wine Jus
description:  In Collaboration with Colman’s - Fire up your bangers with Colman's mustard.

This Cumberland Sausages and Potato & Parsnip Mash is bursting full of flavours and makes the perfect dinner night option from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!
